        <span class="dot"></span>
        <div class="timeline-image">
          <img src="/public/images/Screenshot 2026-01-29 at 10.49.18 AM.png" />
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-story">
          <blockquote>
            FORM WITHOUT FUNCTION IS JUST DECORATION
          </blockquote>
          <P class="muted">
            Once structure was clear, I turned to presentation. This project merged my background in physical craftsmanship and design with the digital world. Through CSS, Flexbox, and Grid, I explored balance, spacing, and responsiveness — how a site should feel across devices. It wasn’t about adding effects, but about control. I learned that good design isn’t loud; it’s intentional. Just like a well-made product, it should disappear into use.
          </P>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>           
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="timeline-item three reveal">
        <span class="dot"></span>
        <div class="timeline-image">
